[{"Id": 1013048, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Ibrahim, the Prophet’s (s) son passed away in childhood, which was a very sad event for the Messenger of Allah (s) so much so that with tearful eyes he said: Although the heart is restless in his sorrow we do not say anything that may enrage Allah. This beloved son of the Prophet (s) is buried in Baqi cemetery. One must stand by his grave and recite his Ziyarat as follows…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ibrahim, farzand Rasool-e-Khuda (s) is duniya se kamsini mein rukhsat huwe, jo Rasool (s) ke liye bada dar-naak haadsa tha, keh Unki aankho’n se aansoo behne lage aur unho ne farmaya. “Jab keh is gham mein dil be-qaraar hai, magar ham kuchh nahi kehenge jis se Khuda naraaz ho.” Yeh chaheete farzande Rasool (s) Baqi ke qabrastan mein dafn hai. Unki qabr ke paas khade ho kar is tarah unki ziyarat padhe…", "UrduDescription": "جناب ابراہیم ؑکی قبر کے نزدیک کھڑے ہو کر کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9"